    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, no-fuss daily driver that won't empty your wallet? This fair-condition vehicle is ready to get you where you need to go! As expected from a well-loved car, it shows the typical signs of everyday use \u2014 some cosmetic wear inside and out \u2014 but it runs and drives, making it a great practical choice for budget-conscious buyers. Come take it for a spin and see the value for yourself!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
